quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  12,87,"Ya baniyya ithhaboo fatahassasoomin yoosufa waakheehi wala tay-asoo min rawhi Allahiinnahu la yay-asu min rawhi Allahi illaalqawmu alkafiroon"
  12,88,"Falamma dakhaloo AAalayhi qalooya ayyuha alAAazeezu massana waahlanaaddurru waji/na bibidaAAatin muzjatinfaawfi lana alkayla watasaddaq AAalayna innaAllaha yajzee almutasaddiqeen"
  12,89,"Qala hal AAalimtum mafaAAaltum biyoosufa waakheehi ith antum jahiloon"
  12,90,"Qaloo a-innaka laanta yoosufa qalaana yoosufu wahatha akhee qad manna AllahuAAalayna innahu man yattaqi wayasbir fa-inna Allahala yudeeAAu ajra almuhsineen"
  12,91,"Qaloo tallahi laqad atharakaAllahu AAalayna wa-in kunna lakhati-een"
  12,92,"Qala la tathreeba AAalaykumualyawma yaghfiru Allahu lakum wahuwa arhamu arrahimeen"
  12,93,"Ithhaboo biqameesee hathafaalqoohu AAala wajhi abee ya/ti baseeran wa/tooneebi-ahlikum ajmaAAeen"
  12,94,"Walamma fasalati alAAeeru qalaaboohum innee laajidu reeha yoosufa lawla antufannidoon"
  12,95,"Qaloo tallahi innakalafee dalalika alqadeem"
